253enum SpellSchools
254{
255 SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL = 0,
256 SPELL_SCHOOL_HOLY = 1,
257 SPELL_SCHOOL_FIRE = 2,
258 SPELL_SCHOOL_NATURE = 3,
259 SPELL_SCHOOL_FROST = 4,
260 SPELL_SCHOOL_SHADOW = 5,
261 SPELL_SCHOOL_ARCANE = 6
262};
263
264constexpr auto MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL = 7;
265
266enum SpellSchoolMask
267{
268 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NONE = 0x00, // not exist
269 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL), // PHYSICAL (Armor)
270 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_HOLY = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_HOLY),
271 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FIRE = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_FIRE),
272 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NATURE = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_NATURE),
273 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FROST = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_FROST),
274 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SHADOW = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_SHADOW),
275 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ARCANE = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_ARCANE),
276
277 // unions
278
279 // 124, not include normal and holy damage
280 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL = (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FIRE |
281 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NATURE | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FROST |
282 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SHADOW | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ARCANE),
283 // 126
284 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC = (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_HOLY | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL),
285
286 // 127
287 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ALL = (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC)
288};
289
290inline SpellSchools GetFirstSchoolInMask(SpellSchoolMask mask)
291{
292 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; ++i)
293 if (mask & (1 << i))
294 return SpellSchools(i);
295
296 return SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL;
297}

1583 GO_FLAG_DESTROYED = 0x00000400,
1584};

2806inline uint8 ClassByQuestSort(int32 QuestSort)
2807{
2808 switch (QuestSort)
2809 {
2810 case QUEST_SORT_WARLOCK:
2811 return CLASS_WARLOCK;
2812 case QUEST_SORT_WARRIOR:
2813 return CLASS_WARRIOR;
2814 case QUEST_SORT_SHAMAN:
2815 return CLASS_SHAMAN;
2816 case QUEST_SORT_PALADIN:
2817 return CLASS_PALADIN;
2818 case QUEST_SORT_MAGE:
2819 return CLASS_MAGE;
2820 case QUEST_SORT_ROGUE:
2821 return CLASS_ROGUE;
2822 case QUEST_SORT_HUNTER:
2823 return CLASS_HUNTER;
2824 case QUEST_SORT_PRIEST:
2825 return CLASS_PRIEST;
2826 case QUEST_SORT_DRUID:
2827 return CLASS_DRUID;
2828 case QUEST_SORT_DEATH_KNIGHT:
2829 return CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT;
2830 }
2831 return 0;
2832}

2992inline SkillType SkillByLockType(LockType locktype)
2993{
2994 switch (locktype)
2995 {
2996 case LOCKTYPE_PICKLOCK:
2997 return SKILL_LOCKPICKING;
2998 case LOCKTYPE_HERBALISM:
2999 return SKILL_HERBALISM;
3000 case LOCKTYPE_MINING:
3001 return SKILL_MINING;
3002 case LOCKTYPE_FISHING:
3003 return SKILL_FISHING;
3004 case LOCKTYPE_INSCRIPTION:
3005 return SKILL_INSCRIPTION;
3006 default:
3007 break;
3008 }
3009 return SKILL_NONE;
3010}
